{"tid":2157672,"cid":37,"subCid":0,"title":"九龍站車位大平賣 116萬平過嘉湖山莊車位","createTime":"2020-08-15T07:41:57.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-18T21:46:26.000Z","uid":263581,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"e7d3cd23b0556dbd2265cdad1e92a8f98f1c04ae","tid":2157672,"uid":263581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-15T07:41:57.000Z","msg":"香港前景不明朗，加上疫情影響，有業主急住移民而大平賣車位離場，九龍站車位成交價低見116萬，平過嘉湖山莊車位。<br />\n<br />\n香港置業首席聯席董事戴志文指，九龍站漾日居錄得車位成交，車位為B1層3個單號車位及2個雙號車位，5個車位以總成交價580萬元易手，變相平均每個116萬，<span class=\"red\">平過嘉湖山莊車位</span>。戴志文解釋，由於車位業主趕移民，亦明白同區車位現時「<span class=\"red\">只有價沒有市場</span>」，而且一直無特別成交，故今次平賣離場，最終獲投資者承接。<br />\n<br />\n原業主2008年以184萬購入，現以公司名義轉讓，成交價580萬，帳面大賺400萬。<br />\n<br />\n買唔起九龍站樓買個車位都好<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"336efbd9ee08dab2693cec67eb9833229309755e","tid":2157672,"uid":19552,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-15T07:44:12.000Z","msg":"前排有個何文田六球車位<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4048b03dd333f1cd433ecaf0e61001377c6b4e47","tid":2157672,"uid":221051,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-15T07:57:38.000Z","msg":"即係其實個aa 都知係有價冇市...."},{"pid":"8da9fe2bb89677a2db3e4cddfc288b88ed67c82f","tid":2157672,"uid":58287,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"336efbd9ee08dab2693cec67eb9833229309755e","tid":2157672,"uid":19552,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-15T07:44:12.000Z","msg":"前排有個何文田六球車位<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-15T08:29:03.000Z","msg":"車位最主要講供求。<br />\n供求平行就好難升，相反就會升到CLS。"},{"pid":"7b114ec9775f65451044ca2edb5e53cde8c08495","tid":2157672,"uid":17705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8da9fe2bb89677a2db3e4cddfc288b88ed67c82f","tid":2157672,"uid":58287,"like":0,"dislike